{"article_id":"pqLSaAbYRcCj2tSc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The long-running battle over the Trump administration ' s bid","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to end the Obama-era program for young undocumented immigrants","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"known as \" Dreamers \"","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"will land before the Supreme Court on Tuesday .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"And with a ruling","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"expected in the midst of a presidential election year ,","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"the case puts the high court at the center of one of the most politically charged issues since the start of President Trump ' s term .","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"TRUMP DECISION","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"TO END DACA","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"WAS LAWFUL ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"JUSTICE DEPARTMENT SAYS","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"For the administration and Dreamers alike , it all comes down to the Supreme Court ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"where Trump picks","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and Neil Gorsuch now sit .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Federal appeals courts across the country have rejected efforts","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to phase out the Obama-era program","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"known as Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals , or DACA ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"but the administration has looked to the high court for support .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"`` The administration has basically chalked up the fact","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"that they are going to lose a lot of these cases in the lower courts , ''","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"said Thomas Dupree , a former top Bush Justice Department official and now an appellate attorney .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"`` But they 're playing the long game .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"that there are those in the White House and the Justice Department","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"who have made a calculation","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"saying ,","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"' Look","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"we can absorb all these losses in the lower courts","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"because we are going to win the endgame","depth":16},{"id":30,"text":"when this case gets into the Supreme Court . ' \"","depth":16},{"id":31,"text":"It remains to be seen how the court will rule , however , on this complicated issue","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"-- which concerns the limits of one president","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"trying to rescind the policies of his predecessor .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Created under executive order ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"DACA gives some undocumented immigrants","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"brought to the United States as children","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"the opportunity","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to receive a renewable two-year period of deferred action from deportation","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"and become eligible for a work permit .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"`` The reason","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"the","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"[ Trump administration ]","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"gave","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"was their belief","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"that it was illegal to have such a program","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that gives protected status to a group of people","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"who are not here legally , ''","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"said Paul Smith , a Georgetown Law professor","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"who has argued cases before the Supreme Court .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"`` They were caught between the political reality","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that they did n't want to dump on the Dreamers ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"but they still wanted to get rid of DACA as Obama 's policy . ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"An estimated 700,000 young adults currently in the DACA program could be affected ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"with a ruling for the administration potentially putting them at risk for deportation once again .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"The Trump administration announced its plan","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to phase out the program in 2017 ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"only for the federal courts to rule","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that it could not apply retroactively","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and that DACA should be restarted in full .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"The White House fought back on those decisions ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"the president has broad authority over immigration enforcement policy .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"DACA proponents have argued","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that Trump ' s planned termination violates federal law","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"requiring adequate notice-and-comment periods","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"before certain federal rules are changed ,","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"as well as other constitutional equal protection and due process guarantees .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"The Supreme Court took the unusual step","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"of taking up the cases","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"before they had been fully heard at the lower court level .","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"Those federal courts have issued nationwide injunctions ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"blocking the administration 's plans , at least for now .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"The Trump administration argues","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that the DACA program is not working","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"and is unlawful ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"and that the president should have the `` absolute discretion ''","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"to adopt a revised overall immigration strategy .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"`` Given the unacceptably high numbers of illegal border crossings , ''","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"the Justice Department wrote in its appeal to the Supreme Court ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"`` it was critically important for DHS","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"[ Department of Homeland Security ]","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"to project a message","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"that leaves no doubt","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"regarding the clear , consistent , and transparent enforcement of the immigration laws against all classes and categories of aliens . ''","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"And Attorney General Bill Barr says","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"three separate nationwide injunctions ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"keeping DACA in place for now ,","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"have created chaos in the courts .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"`` Dreamers remain in limbo ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"the political process has been pre-empted ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"and we have had over a year of bitter political division","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"that included a government shutdown of unprecedented length , ''","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"he said in a recent speech .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"`` Meanwhile , the humanitarian crisis at our southern border persists ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"while legislative efforts remain frozen","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"as both sides await the courts ' word on DACA and other immigration issues . ''","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"A dozen states","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"led by Texas","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"are among the parties","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"backing the administration .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"But opponents say","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"the government has given only cursory explanations","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"for justifying DACA 's demise .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"By contrast ,","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"they say ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"the benefits for Dreamers and for the country are indisputable .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"`` These benefits have allowed DACA participants to achieve a 91 percent employment rate , and to increase their wages by 69 percent , ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"said lawyers for the University of California , one of the key plaintiffs .","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"`` Access to lawful work allows DACA participants to support their families ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"including their estimated 200,000 U.S.-citizen children ,","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"and to receive employer-sponsored health insurance . ''","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"A host of civil rights groups filed separate briefs in support , along with several states","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"including New York and California .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"Hundreds of pro-DACA demonstrators are expected to rally Tuesday outside the Supreme Court","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"while arguments are taking place .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"Among those","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"anxiously awaiting the Supreme Court 's decision","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"is Daniela , a college student in Washington , D.C.","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"She asked","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"her last name not be used .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"`` It 's really sad","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"thinking","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"that by the time","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"I graduate","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"I might not even be able to be a teacher , ''","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"she told Fox News in a recent interview .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"`` It 's frustrating for sure .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"And so I really hope","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"that something can change within the next few months . ''","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Daniela has been active on her campus , as president of the Dreamers Alliance , a support system for undocumented students like her ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"promoting immigrant rights .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"She came to the U.S. with her family from El Salvador at age 3 ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"and her dream is to become an educator .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"`` We matter","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"and we 're here","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and we 're not going to stop fighting","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"-- and not fighting in the sense","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"that we 're angry --","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"but fighting in the sense","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"that we need some kind of solution . ''","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"Daniela is getting financial assistance through TheDream.US , the nation 's largest college access program for immigrant youth .","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"The group 's program director says","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"the Supreme Court may be the Dreamers ' last hope .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"SUPREME COURT TO DECIDE","depth":5},{"id":145,"text":"WHETHER TRUMP ADMINISTRATION CAN END DACA PROGRAM","depth":5},{"id":146,"text":"`` For young people","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"waiting and hearing ,","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"and constantly being on pins and needles of these court hearings is very difficult , ''","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"said Gabriela Pacheco .","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"`` It feels for many of them that the rug is being pulled underneath them ,","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"that they 've done everything right","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"that they 're contributing ,","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"they 're going to college","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"and they 're working .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"We all win","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"when you have a young person","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"maximizing their full potential . ''","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"Early in his administration , Trump voiced some support for DACA ,","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"but only if it was tied to congressional negotiations","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"over tightening legal immigration","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"-- and building his border wall .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"`` We are going to deal with DACA with heart , ''","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"Trump said in February 2017 .","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"`` I have to deal with a lot of politicians ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"don ' t forget ,","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"and I have to convince them","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"that what I ' m saying is right . ''","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"Months later , the president announced","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"he was terminating DACA under his own executive authority ,","depth":7},{"id":170,"text":"prompting the flood of lawsuits .","depth":6},{"id":171,"text":"However , one thing","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"the Trump administration and many DACA backers agree on","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"is that Congress could rectify the issue ,","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"by passing a comprehensive immigration reform bill","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"that would include Dreamer protections ,","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"backed by the force of law .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"In the court of popular opinion , DACA remains popular .","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"A Fox News poll in June found","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"73 percent of registered voters","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"surveyed","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"favor allowing Dreamers to stay in the U.S. ,","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"while 24 percent are opposed .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"The consolidated cases are DHS v. Regents of the University of California","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"( 18-587 ) ;","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"Trump v. NAACP","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"( 18-588 ) ;","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"and McAlleenan v. Vidal","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"( 18-589 ) .","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"A ruling is expected by late June 2020 .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":379,"left":196,"right":378,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":193,"right":195,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"